# Rules and Leaders
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# \hrule          c  makes a rule box in vertical mode.
# \vrule          c  makes a rule box in horizontal mode.
# \cleaders       c  insert centered leaders.
# \leaders        c  fill space using specified glue with a box or rule.
